    "title": "This Week's Stream Schedule",
    "hint": "",
    "noteLabel": "A note from Asobu",
    "noteHtml": "<div class=\"sp-wish\" style=\"margin:16px 0;\"><div class=\"sp-wish__body\"><img class=\"sp-wish__icon\" src=\"./mita/icon.png\" alt=\"Mitarai Asobu\"><div class=\"sp-wish__bubble-wrap\"><div class=\"sp-wish__bubble sp-wish__bubble--long\">I’ll hold back on streaming games and keep working hard (teary-eyed). I’ll keep preparing for the anniversary stream this week too, so please make sure to come! Turn on notifications and wait for it 🤍 The coloring contest is still open! Please post with the hashtag #御手洗みたら？ by the 23rd!</div></div></div></div>"
